"Document: gentoo\n"
"Title: Gentoo Manual\n"
"Author: Emil Brink\n"
"Abstract: This manual describes what Gentoo is, and how it can be used.\n"
"Section: File Management\n"
"\n"
"Format: HTML\n"
"Index: /usr/share/doc/gentoo/html/index.html\n"
"Files: /usr/share/doc/gentoo/html/*.html"

#. type: <p></p>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:2003
msgid ""
"For information on the file format, see <manref section=\"8\" name=\"install-"
"docs\"> and the <package>doc-base</package> manual, in <file>/usr/share/doc/"
"doc-base/doc-base.html/</file>."
msgstr ""
"Per informazioni sul formato del file si veda <manref section=\"8\" name="
"\"install-docs\"> ed il manuale <package>doc-base</package> , reperibile in "
"<file>/usr/share/doc/doc-base/doc-base.html/</file>."

#. type: <p></p>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:2005
msgid ""
"For more details on installing additional documentation, look in <ref id="
"\"destdir\">."
msgstr ""
"Per ulteriori dettagli su come installare documentazione aggiuntiva, si veda "
"in <ref id=\"destdir\">."

#. type: <heading></heading>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:2007
msgid "<file>docs</file> file"
msgstr "Il file <file>docs</file>"

#. type: <p></p>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:2010
msgid ""
"This file specifies the file names of documentation files we can have "
"<manref section=\"1\" name=\"dh_installdocs\"> install into the temporary "
"directory for us."
msgstr ""
"Questo file specifica il nome dei file di documentazione che si possono "
"avere <manref section=\"1\" name=\"dh_installdocs\"> li installa nella "
"directory temporanea automaticamente."

#. type: <p></p>
#: maint-guide.en.sgml:2013
msgid ""
"By default, it will include all existing files in the top-level source "
"directory that are called \"<file>BUGS</file>\", \"<file>README*</file>\", "
"\"<file>TODO</file>\" etc."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente, questo file includerà tutti i file esistenti nella directory "
